    @Deprecated
public class JifArrayAccessAssign_c
extends polyglot.ast.ArrayAccessAssign_c
    A ArrayAccessAssign_c represents a Java assignment expression to an array element. For instance, A[3] = e. The class of the Expr returned by ArrayAccessAssign_c.left()is guaranteed to be an ArrayAccess.
